quests.name: Out of Sight, Out of Mind's Eye
quests.description: After the most brutal training, I have become one with the shadows and achieved enlightenment. However, a Tetranadon hinders my training. I will bestow my wisdom upon any who can defeat it.

quests.name: Arena 06
quests.description: Yo, Ace! Ready for some awesome Arena action!? Prove your mettle using the equipment provided here!
quests.objective: Slay a Volvidon, a Basarios, and a Bazelgeuse

quests.name: Challenge Quest 01
quests.description: Sup, Ace? Ready for a REAL challenge? Don't think I'm gonna go easy on ya jast 'cuz you're my favorite. Nah, it's thrash or BE thrashed! If ya know what I mean. Let's see what you got!

quests.name: Arena 03
quests.description: Yo, Ace! Ready for some awesome Arena action!? Prove your mettle using the equipment provided here!
quests.objective: Slay a Royal Ludroth and a Nargacuga

quests.name: Arena 02
quests.description: Yo, Ace! Ready for some awesome Arena action!? Prove your mettle using the equipment provided here!

quests.name: Beast of the Shadows
quests.description: Ah, Hunter! The illustrations I was working on turned out so well that I decided to make them into a stickers! What do you think? Adorable, are they not? Complete my request, and they're yours! Now... hop to it-to it!

quests.name: Heart of a Warrior
quests.description: Hey, Squirt! We've got ourselves a little quest that'll determine who's the strongest hunter. My zenny's on you, but we'll see! All ya gotta do is go smack around a Goss Harag and Magnamalo in the Arena and these titles are yours! Think you're up to it? Well go get to it! Bwahahaha!
quests.objective: Hunt a Goss Harag and Magnamalo

quests.name: I Can't Do What Somnacan
quests.description: I am a professional dancer, and I wish to expand my repertoire with the graceful moves of a Somnacanth! YOU hunt one while I watch safely from afar and take notes. I'll teach you a gesture as a reward!

quests.name: Haste Makes Waste
quests.description: Seems like power alone isn't enough these days -- hunters want to look intelligent too. I'd take brawn over brains any day... I guess times are changing. Complete this request, and I'll give you the required materials.

quests.name: Harvest 'Shroom
quests.description: The fungi around here are no fun, but the Unique Mushrooms from the Deserted Island really satisfy! Be a dear and fetch me some. Ripened or Choice Mushrooms would be nice, too. I hear some 'shrooms will ripen when Altaroth eat 'em!

quests.name: Farm Aid
quests.description: An omery herd of Jaggia's been ravagin' mah farm. The varmints come tearin' through an' eat up everything - roots and all. If you could head on out there ad snuff'em out on their own turf, I'd be much obliged.

quests.name: Guts: It's What's for Dinner
quests.description: Folks call my lord the "Master of Inviting" because of his big shindigs. He's throwing a full-moon banquet for the nobles, and I want to knock their fancy pants off. I need Epioth tripe, ASAP.

quests.name: Prescription Pick-Up
quests.description: Constipation, backaches, performance anxiety - my patients are fallin' apart! Two Kelbi horns would cure 'em all. Just knock the Kelbi out; that makes it a snap to harvest they horns.

quests.name: Goldenfish Opportunity
quests.description: I love fish so much my pals say I should marry one. Silly, huh? Goldenfish are the prettiest.. um, I mean best. Catch me three and I'll reward you well - maybe even invite you to the wedding... I'm kidding!

quests.name: Sunken Treasures
quests.description: I promised my lady a Red Coral Stone hair clip... but water scares me! Now I'm up Dung Creek without a paddle. Dive down and get me some Red Coral Stones so she won't find out I'm a fraidy Felyne!

quests.name: Harvest Tour: Sandy Plains
quests.description: Everyone here, nya? Welcome to the Sandy Plains Harvest Tour, where we'll witness the purrfect beauty of the desert. After two minutes, you can grab a Paw Pass Ticket for safe and easy passage home.
quests.objective: Survive until time expires or deliver a Paw Pass Ticket

quests.name: Bug Hunt
quests.description: I'm considering writing a book about Altaroth in this area, Surely, even illiterate brutes like you hunters have noticed the large size and peculiar traits of these insects. Come, assist in my research!

quests.name: My Lord's Errand
quests.description: Grim tidings. An Arzuros has been seen roaming the Deserted Island. Its appearance is ill timed with my lord's visit, for he is not a spry as he once was. Good hunter, vanguish the Arzuros for the sake of my graybeard liege.

quests.name: Bear Trap
quests.description: A while back, I happened across an Arzuros catching fish in the river. Talk about the one that got away! If we could somehow capture it, I reckon I could use its materials to whip up some fancy fishing gear.

quests.name: Who's The Boss?
quests.description: We know there are - to use a layman's term - "bosses" within Jaggi's herds, but we still have much to learn of their social hierarchy. If you could just obtain a Jaggi leader specimen for me...

quests.name: No Love for Ludroth!
quests.description: I gets riled up just thinkin' about it! Some stupid Ludroth beats me- and I gets fired over it! How was I supposed ta know d'em cute beasties packed such a wallop? How's about you go wallop 'em back for me?

quests.name: Pain in the Plains
quests.description: Not only did that beast whup all us villagers with its army of Jaggi - now it's traipsing around the Sandy Plains like it owns the joint. Insult to injury, that is! Time to call in a professional. Meaning you!

quests.name: Secret of the Crystal Bones
quests.description: You brawny hunter-types scoff at my studies of crystallized bones. Hmph! They have much to say about life in the far past and the mysteries of today! My progress has stalled here on the frontier. You must help!

quests.name: No Guts, No Glory
quests.description: Delex attack in packs and are mean as all get out, but their innards make right good trail chow. I reckon takin' them down is like killin' two Vespoids with one stone, eh? Now git along, little hunter.

quests.name: Harvest Tour: Flooded Forest
quests.description: Everyone here, nya? Welcome to the Flooded Forest Harvest Tour - a purrfect adventure through the trees! You'll receive a Paw Pass Ticket in two minutes for safe, easy passage home.
quests.objective: Survive until time expires or deliver a Paw Pass Ticket

quests.name: Trapping a Trickster
quests.description: No, no, no! I was so close to catching it! And then, I heard this freaky call and - bam! Foiled again! You think you're such a hot hunter, you try catching this sly guy!

quests.name: A Royal Pain
quests.description: Anyone who's anyone in high society has a pet Royal Ludroth. They're so orange! So squishy! I absolutely must have one! Do TRY not to hurt it badly, you brute. I suppose a few minor scrapes are acceptable...

quests.name: Playing with Fire
quests.description: I ran into this saucy little wyvern in the Sandy Plains. Before I knew it, my derriere was on fire! We can't have perverted monsters assaulting women! I want payback... And you're gonna help me get it!

quests.name: Leading the Charge
quests.description: I've read reports of an intriguing monster in the Sandy Plains... Apparently, weak weapons bounce off its tough hide, and the beast sometimes destroys anthills when it charges. Fascinating!

quests.name: Rhenoplos Rampage!
quests.description: Oww... I was out digging for fossils, minding my own business, when this... rock-looking thing hit me where the sun don't shine. The Medicine Man says I can't sit down for a month! Avenge my rear-end!

quests.name: Herbivore Egg Hunt!
quests.description: I want to make family recipe for my tubby hubby, but I'm missing the secret ingredient. (*Psst* It's Herbivore Eggs!) Bring me some, please. You'll find them in the Sandy Plains, under that tree in the oasis.

quests.name: Toxic Troublemaker
quests.description: No sooner had I stepped through the foliage than I spied the creature, standing in a sea of orange beasts. Sure, I could've handled it easy enough, but why hog all the fun? Have at it, hunter!

quests.name: Save Our Boat
quests.description: The Lagiacrus scuttled our huntin' boat, and now we need parts from a Royal Ludroth to get her ship-shape. We just want to make Moga Village prosperous again -it's our duty as the local heroes!

quests.name: Pest Control
quests.description: Bnahabra keep moseyin' from the Flooded Forest and goin' after mah cattle. Spooks'em so bad their milk comes out already sour. Tastes terrible! Reckon you could take care o' them varmint, pardner?

quests.name: The Deadliest Catch
quests.description: Gah! Now I know what it's like to drown on land! We ran into some rough critters the other day that tore the Flooded Forest Guard a new one! They don't pay me enough for this. You handle it!

quests.name: Harvest Tour: Tundra
quests.description: Everyone here, nya? Welcome to the Tundra Harvest Tour. Hope your fur is thick! If you get cold and wanna quit, you'll receive a Paw Pass Ticket in two minutes. Use it for safe, easy passage home.
quests.objective: Survive until time expires or deliver a Paw Pass Ticket

quests.name: Dragon Lady
quests.description: Egad! I'd heard rumors of Rathian sightings, but I never thought they'd be true. That thing's way too tough for my blood! Any warriors worth their swords out there? I beseech you: save our village!

quests.name: Poached Wyvern Eggs
quests.description: I have an urgent request! If I do not serve Wyvern Eggs at the upcoming banquet, I'll be fired -- as in literally set on fire! Save me from becoming the main course and you'll be amply rewarded!

quests.name: Hunter Killer
quests.description: Listen to a hunter who knows! There's a Barroth and a Great Jaggi running wild on the Sandy Plains. No matter how good a hunter you think you are, you'd better stay away. It ain't worth your life!
quests.objective: Hunt a Barroth and a Great Jaggi

quests.name: A Royal Rumble
quests.description: Pardon my discretion in this matter, my good hunter, but my liege lord -- who shall remain nameless -- desires a Rathian of his own. I fear I am not up to the task, but I cannot refuse his request.

quests.name: Accident Investigation
quests.description: It's hard to say exactly what happened... The fog was just so thick. I remember a flash, and then the ship cracked open. We lost every head of cattle! The culprit must be still out there... Mind taking a look?

quests.name: The Snowbound Slider
quests.description: (REPORT BEGINS) Lagombi spotted on the Tundra. (STOP) Requesting immediate support from all qualified hunters. (STOP) We are snowed in and cannot render assistance. (REPORT ENDS)

quests.name: Leader of the Icepack
quests.description: To think those beasts had something like THAT leading them! Our bodyguard was useless! That does it - I'm putting our expedition on indefinite hiatus until someone takes this pack down!

quests.name: The Creeping Venom
quests.description: Look, I ain't no green trainee. I've been around! But I ain't never seen nothin' like THAT. I enter this cave and a second later this... this THING is covering me. Ugh! I'm getting too olf for this!

quests.name: Lost in Blue
quests.description: *Brr* I d-don't think I'll ever f-feel my n-nose agin. I thought they were r-regular Jaggi, but no. They immobilized us. And now my f-face has f-frostbite! Th-those monsters can't be allowed to run free!

quests.name: Cold Stones
quests.description: I tell ya, the Tundra is really somethin'. It's like, the final frontier of excavation! Diggers like me wouldn't last five minutes in the cold, though, so I'm counting on you. Nab me 8 Bloodstones, hunter.

quests.name: Harvest Tour: Volcano
quests.description: Everyone here, nya? Welcome to the Volcano Harvest Tour. Keep an eye out for ore you can only find here! If you get too hot under the collar, you'll receive a Paw Pass Ticket in two minutes. Use it for safe, easy passage home.
quests.objective: Survive until time expires or deliver a Paw Pass Ticket

quests.name: Fell the Lagiacrus!
quests.description: You did good against the Lagiacrus, kid. Now  that ya got a taste of its power, it's time to seal the deal. This'll be the ultimate battle. I have to say, I'm almost jealous. Do us proud, kid.

quests.name: The Desert Gourmand
quests.description: Oy! One minuite I was rattlin' along the Sandy Plains in me barrel buggy, mindin' me own lookout. And then, RAAARRR! Cart goes flyin' -- and me with it! What gives!? The barrel business is s'pposed ta be safe, by gum!

quests.name: The Lord of the Seas
quests.description: Dear hunter: Our institute has launched an intensive study of Lagiacrus, the Lord of the Seas. A live specimen would be a huge boon to our research. Are you willing to put your life on the line for marine science?

quests.name: Hammer Time
quests.description: Heed my words, dear hunter, and you shall prevail. It is said that the Duramboros wields its tail like a hammer, swinging it hither and thither while pounding the earth. May your journey be a safe one, and may it end with a trophy.

quests.name: Walk 'N' Roll
quests.description: Which four-legged beast is also a ball? What red roller sometimes struts its stuff? Why, it's the vicious Volvidon! See for yourself in the Volcano. Just don't let this ball toss you around!

quests.name: Uragaan's Trail
quests.description: I've read of a large beast in the volcanic region with a prominent jaw. I could build a career around such a creature! Even a partial specimen would do. Get to gathering, hunter. Oh, my wit knows no rival.

quests.name: Heat Exhaustion
quests.description: Powderstones hold concentrated volcanic energy. They pack enough heat to forge a monster carapace or hard minerals. Thing is, you can't make them, so I need you to fetch me some. Carrying them is the tricky part!

quests.name: The Decisive Battle
quests.description: [For top-class hunters only] Alert! The great sea drake Ceadeus has been sighted near the Deserted Island. We lack sufficient information to judge its strength. Hunters should put a stop to it, ASAP!

quests.name: The Wrath of Rathalos
quests.description: I seek a hunter of unmatched valor to defeat the King of the Skies. Succeed and receive untold riches. Gathering halls across the land will echo with songs of your deed. Fail and you're on your own, buddy.

quests.name: A Bard's Tale
quests.description: Ever since I was a wee lad, tales of the phantom drake have entranced me... Finally, after a lifetime of searching, I've found the beast in the frozen wastes! Fair hunter, dare you challenge its might?

quests.name: The Horned Wyvern
quests.description: We guards are so scared we can't go back to work! We spotted a huge, two-horned beast in the desert -- a Diablos! That thing's way too dangerous to wander free. Please deal with it -- my career's at stake here!

quests.name: The Omen
quests.description: Saw it swoop down above the ship, we fif, with wings that blotted out the sun... 'Twas the King of the Skies, the flame drgon Rathalos, sure as I'm an old salt! We be needin' a hunter to kill this bad omen!

quests.name: The Volcano's Fury
quests.description: Don't bother readin' any further unless you're a true hunter -- the type who loves that quiver in your guts when you're livin' on the razor's edge. Still with me? Go to the volcano. Somethin's waitin'.

quests.name: Denizen of the Molten Deep
quests.description: The molten heart of the volcano beats with a fell beast. A once-rare wyvern stirs in the lava. Half of my countrymen have perished; the rest live in fear... Please, release my people from this terror!

quests.name: Harvest Tour: Sandy Plains
quests.description: Everyone here, nya? Welcome to the Sandy Plains Harvest Tour, where we'll witness the purrfect beauty of the desert. After two minutes, you can grab a Paw Pass Ticket for safe and easy passage home.
quests.objective: Survive until time expires or deliver a Paw Pass Ticket

quests.name: Harvest Tour: Flooded Forest
quests.description: Everyone here, nya? Welcome to the Flooded Forest Harvest Tour - a purrfect adventure through the trees! You'll receive a Paw Pass Ticket in two minutes for safe, easy passage home.
quests.objective: Survive until time expires or deliver a Paw Pass Ticket

quests.name: Harvest Tour: Misty Peaks
quests.description: Everyone here, nya? Welcome to the Misty Peaks Harvest Tour. The evergreen landscape is a fancy feast for the eyes, and getting back is kitten's play. You'll receive a Paw Pass Ticket in two minutes for safe, easy passage home.
quests.objective: Survive until time expires or deliver a Paw Pass Ticket

quests.name: The Merchant's Mission
quests.description: Gah! Again my cargo is kaput. What use is guard if he no guard nothing? Always, I hire guard! Always, I hear same story: monster too strong! But not immortal, yes? So, you hunt him? I reward. We understand?

quests.name: Current Events
quests.description: What a twist! People on land suddenly soaked to the bone! The soggy victims insist they saw something yellow before their drenching. What could it have been? Hunter, please, help me solve this ridle!

quests.name: Herd Mentality
quests.description: If I was a Great Jaggi, I'd be, like, "Listen here, Pink Rathian! You got a lotta nerve comin' around MY island. Time to show you there's strength in numbers! Bring on the new recruits! Let's hear it for the herd! RAAARRR!"

quests.name: The Jaggia Menace
quests.description: Jeepers! Jaggia have been wreaking havoc on our crops this season! At this rate, we won't have enough food to survive the winter... The Jaggia mist have a big warren nearby -- please, o something about it before we starve!

quests.name: Avenge the Fallen Hunter!
quests.description: Wy weapon... bounced off its hide like a toy. That thing moved... so fast. Before I knew it... I was knocked cold. The Medicine Man says it's... just a scratch, but the pain! Avenge my flesh wound!

quests.name: Desert Warfare
quests.description: This just in: A Rathian has invaded a Barroth's territory. Expect the Sandy Plains to become a battleground within the next few days. The danger zone begins 25 meters from the monsters. Beware of charges and flames!

quests.name: Bye-Bye, Bloome
quests.description: Ah, there's nothing like the Flooded Forest on a cloudy day. The colors are so... subtle! When I spotted that big crimson flower, I was inspired! But I turned my back for one second to set up my easel., and the flower was gone...

quests.name: Toxic Troublemaker
quests.description: No sooner had I stepped through the foliage than I spied the creature. standing in a sea of orange beasts. Sure, I could've handled it easily enough, but why hog all the fun? Have at it, hunter!

quests.name: Hair of the Dog
quests.description: Something ain't right with Daddy. He says he had too much fun last night and just wants to sleep it off. How can "fun" make you feel icky? Get me some Slagtoth Oils from the Flooded Forest so I can mix up some medicine!

quests.name: Pink Queen of the Peaks
quests.description: Twas like no Rathian I ever seen. She had scales the color of a cherry blossom. Attacked us at seas, she did! I know when she be roostin'. If ya be wirth yer salt.

quests.name: Poison Control
quests.description: Well, ain't that typical. I get back from a 10-day hump in the bush, and what's waiting for me? Orders to hunt down a Purple Ludroth! I need some R&R! Mind fielding this one. Guild Hunter?

quests.name: Double Jeopardy
quests.description: Calling all Elite Hunters -- have I got a request for you! Interested in an Arzuros near the village? Wait, don;t answer. How 'bout two of them? That oughta put some pep in your step! You need more info? No? OK then!

quests.name: Field Trip
quests.description: The next generation of hunters needs your help! Mind sharing your killer skills with my herd of little pupils? Just go hunt the Great Jaggi pack in the Misty Peaks. C'mon, do it for the children.

quests.name: Bully the Bullfango
quests.description: Ugh! My backside's seen better days. Blame the Bullfango! My mom sent me to the Misty Peaks to dig up mushrooms, see, and all of a sudden those beasts were behind me! Long story short, my butt needs avenging!

quests.name: Under the Yolk
quests.description: It's my daughter's birthday, but she thinks I forgot! I shooed her away on errands so I can whip up a Gargwa Egg omelette -- her favorite! I can't wait to see the look on her face! Please, get me the eggs or my surprise will backfire.

quests.name: Siren's Song
quests.description: Its call can summon. Its call can heal. Whose call, you ask? Why, the Qurupeco's, of course. And it has come a-calling on the Deserted Island. Several of them, in fact! Can you resist this creature's siren song?
quests.objective: Survive until time expires or deliver a Paw Pass Ticket

quests.name: Harvest Tour: Tundra
quests.description: Everyone here, nya? Welcome to the Tundra Harvest Tour. Hope your fur is thick! If you get cold and wanna quit, you'll receive a Paw Pass Ticket in two minutes. Use it for safe, easy passage home.
quests.objective: Survive until time expires or deliver a Paw Pass Ticket

quests.name: Splash Damage
quests.description: I seen this black shape in the water, all hige and scary. 'Fore I knew it, a big ol' Piscine Wyvern breached the brine like some kinda flyin' fish. Its splash was like a tidal wave. Soaked me to the britches, it did!

quests.name: Rockslide
quests.description: Holy moly! I was scared enough when I saw those two red boulders bearing down on my head, but it turns out they were monsters! That kind of nonsense is rotten for business. Get rid of 'em!

quests.name: Scene of the Crime
quests.description: Oh, it's tragic! Tragic! There's a Gobul in the Flooded Forest! It tore up me mates! And now trade in the region is ruined. Somebody, anybody, please... Stop the beast 'fore it 'urts anyone else!

quests.name: Snowball Fight
quests.description: We've had recent reports of a monster rampaging across the Tundra, flinging snowballs with the force of an avalanche. People are getting hurt our there. Investigate at once!

quests.name: Snowball Fight
quests.description: I'm reporting live from the Tundra, where two Lagombi are making their way across the frozen landscape with all the grace of ice ballerinas I could stand here and watch them all day!... Wait, are they coming this way! RUN!

quests.name: Leader of the Icepack
quests.description: To think those beasts had something like THAT leading them! Our bodyguard was useless! That does it -- I'm putting our expedition on indefinite hiatus until someone takes this pack down!

quests.name: Shocking Development
quests.description: Attention, Elite Hunters! This request is tailor made for your skills! Apparently there's this terrible Thunder element monster out on the Tundra. Interested? I sure am! Who wouldn't be, you know? Well, I suppose (TRUNCATED)

quests.name: Research Assistance
quests.description: Egad! Our antidote research has hit a brick wall. We can't reach the next phase without dissecting a Gigginox and a Baleful Gigginox. And until we've perfected our medicine, you better remember your Antidotes!
quests.objective: Hunt a Gigginox and a Baleful Gigginox

quests.name: Designer Antlers
quests.description: I finally finished sprucing up my house, but it's still missing that final touch. I figure a giant ornament would be the Felyne's pajamas! Nab me 5 Anteka Antlers for materials. They're easy to carve if you stun the Anteka.

quests.name: Toxin Avenger
quests.description: Eureka! Our antidote research is on the verge of a breakthrough! We just need copious quantities of toxins. I hear several Gigginox have moved to the Tundra... You know what to do, hunter!

quests.name: The Write Stuff
quests.description: Whoever said the pen is mightier than the sword never had to fight a Jade Barroth and a Gigginox with nothing but a quill and ink! Hunters, head to the Tundra posthaste. Tales of your victory shall be writ large!

quests.name: Rumble in the Great Desert
quests.description: Callin' all hunters and Dragonships! The Jhen Mohran -- that sultan of the desert sands -- is upon us! We gotta hit it with guns blazin'! You fancy yerself an ultimate hunter? Then hop aboard, 'cause this is the ultimate hunt!
quests.objective: Slay a Jhen Mohran or repel it

quests.name: Harvest Tour: Volcano
quests.description: Everyone here, nya? Welcome to the Volcano Harvest Tour. Keep an eye out for ore you can only find here! If you get too hot under the collar, you'll receive a Paw Pass Ticket in two minutes. Use it for safe, easy passage home.
quests.objective: Survive until time expires or deliver a Paw Pass Ticket

quests.name: Masked Robbery
quests.description: Yam-BA! Kayamba finally track own rotten Rathalos that swiped precious mask! No way Kayamba dodge fire breath alone, so he bring you along as distraction. Kayamba strategical genius.

quests.name: The Fisherman's Fiend
quests.description: I've learned the most dreadful financial news! The Lagiacrus has appeared in own waters. That beast will destroy the fishery! I'll pay anything if you save our economy... Oh, and the people, too. Right.

quests.name: Troubled Waters
quests.description: As if that phony flyin' fish weren't bad enough, now it's partnered up with a Lagiacrus! Made the'selves at home in my fishin' ground, they did. Left us fisherfolk high and dry. Mind gettin' us out of this fix?
quests.objective: Hunt a Lagiacrus and a Plesioth

quests.name: The Horned Wyvern
quests.description: We guards are so scared we can't go back to work! We spotted a hige, two-horned beast in the desert -- a Diablos! That thing's way too dangerous to wander free. Please deal with it -- my career's at stake here!

quests.name: The Desert Gourmand
quests.description: Oy! One minute I was rattlin' along the Sandy Plains ibn me barrel buggy, mindin' me own lookout. An then, RAAARRR! Cart goes flyin' -- and me with it! What gives!? The barrel business is s'ppose ta be safe, by gum!

quests.name: The Lost Expedition
quests.description: I'm worried, hunter. We havn't heard a peep from one of our Tundra-expedition teams. Mind investigating? It's a cold, cruel region, so gird those loins before you go! Pave the way for our exploration.

quests.name: Denizen of the Molten Deep
quests.description: The molten heart of the volcano beats with a fell beast. A once-rare wyvern stirs in the lava. Half of my countrymen have perished; the rest live in fear... Please, release my people from this terror!

quests.name: The Volcano's Fury
quests.description: Don't bother readin' any further unless you're a true hunter -- the type who loves that quiver in your guts when you're livin' on the razor's edge. Still with me? Go to the volcano. Somethin's waitin'.

quests.name: The Moving Mountain
quests.description: That little moss-covered hill at the Misty Peaks was just begging to be painted. But the second I pulled out my easel and brush, it was gone! How can I be a landscape artist if the landscape won't cooperate?

quests.name: Twin Peaks
quests.description: Ladies like more than long walks on the beach, ya know. I took my date to the Misty Peaks for a little rainy-day romance, but I never thought we'd run into a mammoth beast like that! Twins, even! Can't you help a fella out?

quests.name: [Canteen] The Endless Hunt
quests.description: This battle in the Flooded Forest is gonna be a real quagmire, but it ain't my style to turn tail and run. Help us, and I'll think about tossing in some healthy grub with your reward. I know these soggy operations burn through supplies.

quests.name: Clobberin' Time!
quests.description: When monsters go to sleep at night, they check under the bed for me. I'm just that good! But I done bad. How was I suppose to know those beasts would keep coming? They have a deathwish? Finish what I started, hunter!

quests.name: "Brachydios" Means Trouble
quests.description: Uwasa tell me about new monster -- Brachydios! So I seek it out at Volcano. Very big monster, very violent, very kowai. "Kowai" means scary! You goran for yourself, you hear its DOKAAAAAN! Mayhap bring extra pair dry britches.

quests.name: Azure Attack
quests.description: I was out diggin' for ore when I nearly tripped over an Azure Rathalos. That got my blood flowin'! I ran halfway home before I realized I needed his materials for crafting. I don't care how tough that thing is -- sic 'em!

quests.name: Desert Storm
quests.description: [REPORT BEGINS] A Sand Barioth has been spotted on the Sandy Plains. [STOP] Requesting immediate support from all available skilled hunters. [STOP] The situation is spiraling out of controll... [REPORT ENDS]

quests.name: Jumping At Shadows
quests.description: I saw it! I swear! It was some kinda shadow jumping from tree to tree! It's coming to attack our village -- I just know it -- but no one believes me... Please, hunter, save our village!

quests.name: Howl at the Moon
quests.description: Heed my wors, hunter. It is said that a Zinogre roams the forests on the Misty Peaks. The village must deal with this threat before it causes any more damage! Help us, good hunter, and may your journey be a safe one.

quests.name: Triple Threat
quests.description: I paid a visit to a village in the Sandy Plains -- and found the people in panic! Who could blame them? Not one, not two, but three ferocious monsters were sighted nearby! Would you be so kind as to rid the villagers of this menace?

quests.name: Operation: Paradise Lost
quests.description: Why ain't I surprised? Just when my tour of duty's about to end, I get orders to wipe out all the monsters on the Deserted Island. Typical! I'll do my best, but maybe you could help me get home early, Guild Hunter!

quests.name: Lurkers in the Woods
quests.description: In the deepest forest of the Misty Peaks, natural predators lurk in the shadows, awaiting your approach. The hunter or the hunted... Which will you be?

quests.name: Triumph of the Tyrants
quests.description: What was I thinking? I threw all my troops against the two tyrants in the Sandy Plains, but it wasn't enough. Our reputation is ruined! Hunt them down before I decide to fall on my sword!
quests.objective: Hunt a Diablos and a Black Diablos

quests.name: Frozen Bloodlust
quests.description: We've lost both the earth and the sky on the Tundra. We'll lose the people next if this continues. There is nothing more we can do. Please, drive the two beasts away as quickly as possible!
quests.objective: Hunt a Glacial Agnaktor and a Barioth

quests.name: Heaven and Earth
quests.description: Veteran hunters know that tracking a Rathalos AND a Rathian isn't just a job -- it's an adventure. And during mating season, it's suicide! The slightest slip could kill. Are you up to the challenge?
quests.objective: Hunt a Pink Rathian and an Azure Rathalos

quests.name: Midnight Madness
quests.description: With mine own eyes, I saw its hateful glare and glimmering body. With mine own ears, I heard a roar that shattered the midnight clam. Dare you face the creature before it stains the Sandy Plains red?

quests.name: Ace in the Hole
quests.description: I got a line on a sure bet, but I need Steel Uragaan parts as my trump card. Somebody, anybody, head to the Volcano and hunt one. My life savings is on the line!

quests.name: Echo Location
quests.description: The ear-splitting crack of calving glaciers! The rumbling echo of colliding icebergs! The sounds pf the Tundra stir my soul. I must recreate them in my music! Would you escort me on an expedition to that frozen land?
